1
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:07,000
[SPEAKER_00] Zovem se Matej,imam 27 godina i dolazim iz Slavonskog broda.

2
00:00:07,000 --> 00:00:12,000
[SPEAKER_00] U domu molitve sam sada već sedma godina.

3
00:00:12,000 --> 00:00:17,000
[SPEAKER_00] Kao dijete u mojoj obitelji se nije živa vjera,

4
00:00:17,000 --> 00:00:21,000
[SPEAKER_00] tako da nisam gotovo ništa znao ni o Bogu ni odnosu s Bogom.

5
00:00:21,000 --> 00:00:26,000
[SPEAKER_00] Imao sam eto tu milost da su mi roditelji bili katolici,

6
00:00:26,000 --> 00:00:30,000
[SPEAKER_00] ja to volim reći na papiru.

7
00:00:30,000 --> 00:00:33,000
[SPEAKER_00] Tek toliko znači da su imali sakramente i to je to.

8
00:00:33,000 --> 00:00:37,000
[SPEAKER_00] Tako sam ja za vrijeme svog odrastanja.

9
00:00:37,000 --> 00:00:42,000
[SPEAKER_00] Da primim prvu priče, škrizmu i ništa više.

10
00:00:42,000 --> 00:00:44,000
[SPEAKER_00] I...

11
00:00:44,000 --> 00:00:48,000
[SPEAKER_00] Djetinstvo je bilo poprilično običajeno.

12
00:00:48,000 --> 00:00:51,000
[SPEAKER_00] Tu ne bih ti on ništa posebno izdvajati.

13
00:00:51,000 --> 00:00:53,000
[SPEAKER_00] Kad sam krenuo u srednju školu,

14
00:00:53,000 --> 00:00:55,000
[SPEAKER_00] tad se moj život počeo mijenjati.

15
00:00:55,000 --> 00:01:01,000
[SPEAKER_00] Osjećao sam u sebi veliku prazninu već tada.

16
00:01:01,000 --> 00:01:06,000
[SPEAKER_00] I mogu raditi da sam se tada na glavu bacio u grijeh.

17
00:01:06,000 --> 00:01:13,000
[SPEAKER_00] Tražio sam ljubav, mir, ugodu.

18
00:01:13,000 --> 00:01:16,000
[SPEAKER_00] na krivim mjestima.

19
00:01:16,000 --> 00:01:25,000
[SPEAKER_00] I to je završilo tako da bi često znao i više dana zaredom izlaziti, opijati se.

20
00:01:25,000 --> 00:01:28,000
[SPEAKER_00] Posebno sam volio kasnije marihuanu pušiti.

21
00:01:28,000 --> 00:01:31,000
[SPEAKER_00] Bio sam problematičan, buntovan.

22
00:01:31,000 --> 00:01:37,000
[SPEAKER_00] Živio sam jedan skroz profulan i isprazni život.

23
00:01:37,000 --> 00:01:43,000
[SPEAKER_00] i čak sam joj u školi izgubio jedno godinu.

24
00:01:43,000 --> 00:01:47,000
[SPEAKER_00] Ne zato što sam glup, nego što sam bio jako ljeni neodgovoran.

25
00:01:47,000 --> 00:01:49,000
[SPEAKER_00] Nije mi se dalo otisni u školu.

26
00:01:49,000 --> 00:01:51,000
[SPEAKER_00] Pa onda problemi kod kuća s roditeljima.

27
00:01:51,000 --> 00:01:59,000
[SPEAKER_00] I onda dolazi period kada završavam školu

28
00:01:59,000 --> 00:02:07,000
[SPEAKER_00] i krećem u svom životu osjećat posljedice grijeha.

29
00:02:07,000 --> 00:02:09,000
[SPEAKER_00] Kao nikad prije.

30
00:02:09,000 --> 00:02:14,000
[SPEAKER_00] Taj period je bio, kada mi je bilo 20 godina,

31
00:02:14,000 --> 00:02:19,000
[SPEAKER_00] kad sam se zaposlio i krenio sam razmišljati o tome

32
00:02:19,000 --> 00:02:24,000
[SPEAKER_00] kako ću jednog dana, ok, sada ću sam ostali tu skoro,

33
00:02:24,000 --> 00:02:26,000
[SPEAKER_00] htio sam oteći od svoj obitelji.

34
00:02:26,000 --> 00:02:30,000
[SPEAKER_00] I razmišljao sam, ok, ženit ću se,

35
00:02:30,000 --> 00:02:32,000
[SPEAKER_00] dobit ću jednog dana djecu.

36
00:02:32,000 --> 00:02:38,000
[SPEAKER_00] Ali je li to sve o čemu se ovaj život sastoji?

37
00:02:38,000 --> 00:02:40,000
[SPEAKER_00] Jer je to ono najbitnije?

38
00:02:40,000 --> 00:02:42,000
[SPEAKER_00] Nešto mi je falilo.

39
00:02:42,000 --> 00:02:48,000
[SPEAKER_00] Osjećao sam da ni to ne može ispuniti tu prazniju u meni.

40
00:02:48,000 --> 00:02:52,000
[SPEAKER_00] I u tom periodu je Bog dopustio.

41
00:02:54,000 --> 00:02:58,000
[SPEAKER_00] Da se posljedice grijeha jako odrazi na mene.

42
00:02:58,000 --> 00:03:02,000
[SPEAKER_00] Počeo sam imati noćne more, gotovo svako večer.

43
00:03:02,000 --> 00:03:06,000
[SPEAKER_00] Paralize sna, demonska tlačenja, gušenja.

44
00:03:06,000 --> 00:03:14,000
[SPEAKER_00] Moje tijelo je počeo imati razne bolove,

45
00:03:14,000 --> 00:03:18,000
[SPEAKER_00] glavobolje, strašne bolove u leđima.

46
00:03:18,000 --> 00:03:20,000
[SPEAKER_00] Išija se.

47
00:03:20,000 --> 00:03:22,000
[SPEAKER_00] Počeo sam povraćati.

48
00:03:22,000 --> 00:03:26,000
[SPEAKER_00] Ali to nije bilo da povratiš normalno.

49
00:03:26,000 --> 00:03:30,000
[SPEAKER_00] Jednostavno sam u tom jednom periodu koji je trebalo mjeseci i po dana

50
00:03:30,000 --> 00:03:32,000
[SPEAKER_00] izgubio tek.

51
00:03:32,000 --> 00:03:36,000
[SPEAKER_00] I stalno sam povraćao kao neku sluz.

52
00:03:36,000 --> 00:03:39,000
[SPEAKER_00] Ništa, što god pojedem, sup, ali nešto malo.

53
00:03:39,000 --> 00:03:41,000
[SPEAKER_00] Ma ništa, odmah sve vano.

54
00:03:41,000 --> 00:03:48,000
[SPEAKER_00] Borbe sa anksioznosti, depresijom.

55
00:03:48,000 --> 00:03:50,000
[SPEAKER_00] Jako sam se izolirao u tom periodu.

56
00:03:50,000 --> 00:03:56,000
[SPEAKER_00] I jedini mir koji sam pokušavao naći,

57
00:03:56,000 --> 00:03:59,000
[SPEAKER_00] kako sam ga znao tada naći, je bilo da bi se zatvorio sobu

58
00:03:59,000 --> 00:04:01,000
[SPEAKER_00] i pušio marihuanu.

59
00:04:01,000 --> 00:04:03,000
[SPEAKER_00] Znao sam da je to lažni mir,

60
00:04:03,000 --> 00:04:05,000
[SPEAKER_00] da je to lažna radost, taj osjećaj haja,

61
00:04:05,000 --> 00:04:07,000
[SPEAKER_00] ali ja nisam znao za bolje.

62
00:04:07,000 --> 00:04:09,000
[SPEAKER_00] I niko mi nije govorio.

63
00:04:09,000 --> 00:04:11,000
[SPEAKER_00] Ni da postoji Bog,

64
00:04:11,000 --> 00:04:16,000
[SPEAKER_00] ni niti me iko pokušavao na neki način iščupati svega toga.

65
00:04:16,000 --> 00:04:19,000
[SPEAKER_00] Našao sam se sam u tome.

66
00:04:19,000 --> 00:04:25,000
[SPEAKER_00] I onda su stvari postale čak još gore do te mjere da sam,

67
00:04:25,000 --> 00:04:27,000
[SPEAKER_00] sjećam se jedne večeri,

68
00:04:27,000 --> 00:04:29,000
[SPEAKER_00] dok sam spavao,

69
00:04:29,000 --> 00:04:31,000
[SPEAKER_00] otvorim oči

70
00:04:31,000 --> 00:04:34,000
[SPEAKER_00] i vidim demona kako leti iznad mene.

71
00:04:34,000 --> 00:04:37,000
[SPEAKER_00] Zaletio se na mene i krenio me gužiti.

72
00:04:37,000 --> 00:04:41,000
[SPEAKER_00] Ja sam se skroz izbezumi, nisam znao šta se dešava.

73
00:04:41,000 --> 00:04:44,000
[SPEAKER_00] I kasnije sam otišao nakon toga,

74
00:04:44,000 --> 00:04:45,000
[SPEAKER_00] kada je to prestalo,

75
00:04:45,000 --> 00:04:47,000
[SPEAKER_00] pogledao se na ogledalo,

76
00:04:47,000 --> 00:04:50,000
[SPEAKER_00] na vratu sam imao plave otiske,

77
00:04:50,000 --> 00:04:53,000
[SPEAKER_00] koja da me neko fizički gušio.

78
00:04:53,000 --> 00:04:56,000
[SPEAKER_00] Stvarno sam se pitao što mi se dešava.

79
00:04:57,000 --> 00:04:59,000
[SPEAKER_00] I sam lud.

80
00:04:59,000 --> 00:05:01,000
[SPEAKER_00] Niko mi nije govorio ništa o duhovnom svijetu.

81
00:05:01,000 --> 00:05:04,000
[SPEAKER_00] I kako sam to počeo povraćati,

82
00:05:04,000 --> 00:05:05,000
[SPEAKER_00] moje tijelo postalo jako slabo.

83
00:05:05,000 --> 00:05:07,000
[SPEAKER_00] Nakon mjesec ipo izgubio sam 13 kila

84
00:05:07,000 --> 00:05:10,000
[SPEAKER_00] i završio sam u bolnici.

85
00:05:10,000 --> 00:05:15,000
[SPEAKER_00] I u tem trenutku u bolnici dok sam nežao na krevetu,

86
00:05:15,000 --> 00:05:19,000
[SPEAKER_00] odjedna sam počeo osjećati kako se moje tijelo gasi.

87
00:05:20,000 --> 00:05:22,000
[SPEAKER_00] Počeo je trnuti.

88
00:05:22,000 --> 00:05:26,000
[SPEAKER_00] Osjetio sam trnce od nogu kako se penju gore.

89
00:05:26,000 --> 00:05:29,000
[SPEAKER_00] Gubiš totalno osjećaj postaviti tijelo kao kamena.

90
00:05:29,000 --> 00:05:31,000
[SPEAKER_00] Ko da izglediš iz njega.

91
00:05:35,000 --> 00:05:37,000
[SPEAKER_00] Došao je trenutak kad sam spoznao

92
00:05:37,000 --> 00:05:39,000
[SPEAKER_00] ja ću sada umrati.

93
00:05:39,000 --> 00:05:45,000
[SPEAKER_00] Dva osjećaja su me tada prošlo.

94
00:05:46,000 --> 00:05:48,000
[SPEAKER_00] jedan jako sam se uplašio.

95
00:05:48,000 --> 00:05:50,000
[SPEAKER_00] Da nisam znao šta me čeka sad,

96
00:05:50,000 --> 00:05:52,000
[SPEAKER_00] nakon ove smrti.

97
00:05:52,000 --> 00:05:57,000
[SPEAKER_00] Jer sam osjetio da sam ja u tijelu.

98
00:05:57,000 --> 00:06:00,000
[SPEAKER_00] Spoznao sam da nisam sam u tijelu,

99
00:06:00,000 --> 00:06:02,000
[SPEAKER_00] da imam dušu i da ona će neko dotići.

100
00:06:02,000 --> 00:06:07,000
[SPEAKER_00] A druga stvar koju sam osjetio je

101
00:06:07,000 --> 00:06:10,000
[SPEAKER_00] da sam u jednu ruku bio sretan.

102
00:06:10,000 --> 00:06:15,000
[SPEAKER_00] Jer napokon ovaj život koji me nije ispunjavao,

103
00:06:15,000 --> 00:06:17,000
[SPEAKER_00] koji me nije zadovoljavao,

104
00:06:17,000 --> 00:06:20,000
[SPEAKER_00] koji mi je više manje bio samo patnja

105
00:06:20,000 --> 00:06:24,000
[SPEAKER_00] i nisam ga čak ni smatrao vrijednim življenja će završiti.

106
00:06:24,000 --> 00:06:25,000
[SPEAKER_00] Osjećao sam jedno umakšanje.

107
00:06:25,000 --> 00:06:27,000
[SPEAKER_00] Bog toga.

108
00:06:27,000 --> 00:06:30,000
[SPEAKER_00] I duboko u srcu sam u tom trenutku

109
00:06:30,000 --> 00:06:32,000
[SPEAKER_00] što je čista milost Božja.

110
00:06:32,000 --> 00:06:36,000
[SPEAKER_00] Jer nisam imao nikakav odnos s Bogom.

111
00:06:36,000 --> 00:06:39,000
[SPEAKER_00] I nikad ništa u životu do tada nisam napravio za Boga.

112
00:06:39,000 --> 00:06:41,000
[SPEAKER_00] A sam duboko u srcu.

113
00:06:41,000 --> 00:06:43,000
[SPEAKER_00] Nisam mogao ni govoriti.

114
00:06:43,000 --> 00:06:45,000
[SPEAKER_00] Skroz sam utrnio. Tilo mi se oduzelo.

115
00:06:45,000 --> 00:06:48,000
[SPEAKER_00] I duboko u srcu sam rekao:

116
00:06:48,000 --> 00:06:52,000
[SPEAKER_00] Bože, oprosti mi.

117
00:06:52,000 --> 00:06:53,000
[SPEAKER_00] Ja sam pokušao.

118
00:06:54,000 --> 00:06:58,000
[SPEAKER_00] A sad te molim: uzmi me k sebi.

119
00:06:58,000 --> 00:07:05,000
[SPEAKER_00] Nakon toga, sljedeći trenutak,

120
00:07:05,000 --> 00:07:08,000
[SPEAKER_00] milo se Bože izla na mene.

121
00:07:10,000 --> 00:07:12,000
[SPEAKER_00] Ne mogu se sjetiti imena ne napravila.

122
00:07:12,000 --> 00:07:15,000
[SPEAKER_00] Ka, kad vas prikopčaju, na struji kad vas oživljavaju.

123
00:07:15,000 --> 00:07:18,000
[SPEAKER_00] Doslovno je moje tilo poskočilo od sile.

124
00:07:21,000 --> 00:07:26,000
[SPEAKER_00] I osjetio sam da sam u tom momentu ozdravio.

125
00:07:26,000 --> 00:07:30,000
[SPEAKER_00] Te su svi tereti koje sam tada osjećao spali sa mene.

126
00:07:30,000 --> 00:07:36,000
[SPEAKER_00] A glasovi koji su mi govorili, koji su me tlačili mjesecima prije toga.

127
00:07:38,000 --> 00:07:40,000
[SPEAKER_00] I ti zlodosi koji su mi šaptali uho.

128
00:07:40,000 --> 00:07:42,000
[SPEAKER_00] Ubij se, nisi vrijedan.

129
00:07:42,000 --> 00:07:43,000
[SPEAKER_00] Nikad se nećeš uspjeti promijeniti.

130
00:07:43,000 --> 00:07:45,000
[SPEAKER_00] Tvoj život nema smisla.

131
00:07:45,000 --> 00:07:48,000
[SPEAKER_00] Slične stvari su pobjegli.

132
00:07:48,000 --> 00:07:53,000
[SPEAKER_00] Ja sam otvorio samo oči i...

133
00:07:53,000 --> 00:07:55,000
[SPEAKER_00] Šta se sad desilo?

134
00:07:55,000 --> 00:07:57,000
[SPEAKER_00] Jesam živ?

135
00:07:57,000 --> 00:07:59,000
[SPEAKER_00] Jesam mrtav?

136
00:07:59,000 --> 00:08:02,000
[SPEAKER_00] Gledam oko sebe, nigdje nikoga.

137
00:08:02,000 --> 00:08:04,000
[SPEAKER_00] I samo čujem glas izvana.

138
00:08:05,000 --> 00:08:07,000
[SPEAKER_00] Sve će biti u redu.

139
00:08:07,000 --> 00:08:09,000
[SPEAKER_00] Nisi još gotov.

140
00:08:09,000 --> 00:08:14,000
[SPEAKER_00] Pitao sam se...

141
00:08:14,000 --> 00:08:16,000
[SPEAKER_00] Što je sada ovo?

142
00:08:16,000 --> 00:08:19,000
[SPEAKER_00] Znam da sam se obratio Bogu.

143
00:08:19,000 --> 00:08:21,000
[SPEAKER_00] A ko je Bog?

144
00:08:21,000 --> 00:08:24,000
[SPEAKER_00] Kome sam se točno obratio?

145
00:08:24,000 --> 00:08:27,000
[SPEAKER_00] Kome se to smilovao?

146
00:08:27,000 --> 00:08:28,000
[SPEAKER_00] Kome je to pogodao?

147
00:08:28,000 --> 00:08:29,000
[SPEAKER_00] Kome je to dotakao?

148
00:08:29,000 --> 00:08:30,000
[SPEAKER_00] Kome je to ozdravio?

149
00:08:30,000 --> 00:08:31,000
[SPEAKER_00] Kome je to poštedio život?

150
00:08:31,000 --> 00:08:33,000
[SPEAKER_00] Kome je to obranio dovi tlačitelja?

151
00:08:34,000 --> 00:08:36,000
[UNKNOWN] Pitao sam se...

152
00:08:36,000 --> 00:08:38,000
[SPEAKER_00] Što je istina?

153
00:08:38,000 --> 00:08:39,000
[SPEAKER_00] Ko je istina?

154
00:08:39,000 --> 00:08:40,000
[SPEAKER_00] Gdje je on?

155
00:08:40,000 --> 00:08:41,000
[SPEAKER_00] Šta on radi?

156
00:08:41,000 --> 00:08:42,000
[SPEAKER_00] Kako se on zove?

157
00:08:42,000 --> 00:08:44,000
[SPEAKER_00] Nisam rekao Isuse u tom trenutku.

158
00:08:44,000 --> 00:08:47,000
[SPEAKER_00] Kad sam zavapio i zazao Boga.

159
00:08:47,000 --> 00:08:48,000
[SPEAKER_00] Rekao sam Bože.

160
00:08:48,000 --> 00:08:51,000
[SPEAKER_00] Neki kažu da je Allah Bog.

161
00:08:51,000 --> 00:08:53,000
[SPEAKER_00] Neki kažu da je Buda.

162
00:08:53,000 --> 00:08:56,000
[SPEAKER_00] Na Google ima preko 4000 religija.

163
00:08:56,000 --> 00:08:58,000
[SPEAKER_00] To je prvo mjesto gdje sam otišao gledati.

164
00:08:58,000 --> 00:08:59,000
[SPEAKER_00] Da bih spoznao istinu.

165
00:08:59,000 --> 00:09:01,000
[SPEAKER_00] Gotovo 5000.

166
00:09:01,000 --> 00:09:03,000
[SPEAKER_00] Pa ti sad znaš.

167
00:09:03,000 --> 00:09:07,000
[SPEAKER_00] I tu je krenula moja potraga za Bogom.

168
00:09:11,000 --> 00:09:16,000
[SPEAKER_00] Bog me u tom istraživanju...

169
00:09:16,000 --> 00:09:17,000
[SPEAKER_00] Svatav sam čitao.

170
00:09:17,000 --> 00:09:18,000
[SPEAKER_00] Svatav sam čitao.

171
00:09:18,000 --> 00:09:19,000
[SPEAKER_00] Svatav sam proćavao u tom periodu.

172
00:09:19,000 --> 00:09:23,000
[SPEAKER_00] I...

173
00:09:23,000 --> 00:09:25,000
[SPEAKER_00] Doveo me do toga...

174
00:09:25,000 --> 00:09:27,000
[SPEAKER_00] Do informacije da je molitva razgovor Bogom.

175
00:09:27,000 --> 00:09:28,000
[SPEAKER_00] Pa sam došao do zaključka.

176
00:09:28,000 --> 00:09:29,000
[SPEAKER_00] Ok.

177
00:09:29,000 --> 00:09:31,000
[SPEAKER_00] Ja sam se to vjerovatno pomolio.

178
00:09:31,000 --> 00:09:33,000
[SPEAKER_00] Kad sam mu bio zavapio.

179
00:09:33,000 --> 00:09:35,000
[SPEAKER_00] I odlučio sam otići u crkvu.

180
00:09:35,000 --> 00:09:37,000
[SPEAKER_00] Nakon dugo godina.

181
00:09:37,000 --> 00:09:39,000
[SPEAKER_00] Utišao sam u crkvu.

182
00:09:39,000 --> 00:09:41,000
[SPEAKER_00] Bila je sveta misla.

183
00:09:41,000 --> 00:09:42,000
[SPEAKER_00] Tamo ne počela.

184
00:09:42,000 --> 00:09:45,000
[SPEAKER_00] Kad sam ušao unutra.

185
00:09:45,000 --> 00:09:47,000
[SPEAKER_00] Odmah sam osjetio.

186
00:09:47,000 --> 00:09:50,000
[SPEAKER_00] Nisam znao šta.

187
00:09:50,000 --> 00:09:51,000
[SPEAKER_00] Znam da je to Boža prisutnost bila.

188
00:09:51,000 --> 00:09:53,000
[SPEAKER_00] Tato nisam poznao.

189
00:09:56,000 --> 00:09:57,000
[SPEAKER_00] Pogledao sam.

190
00:09:57,000 --> 00:09:58,000
[SPEAKER_00] Desno od sebe.

191
00:09:58,000 --> 00:10:02,000
[SPEAKER_00] Na zidu je bio okviren jedan tekst iz evanđelja.

192
00:10:02,000 --> 00:10:05,000
[SPEAKER_00] To su bila blaženstva i...

193
00:10:05,000 --> 00:10:09,000
[SPEAKER_00] Krenula se da šalavati vizija u duhu.

194
00:10:09,000 --> 00:10:12,000
[SPEAKER_00] Prvo se...

195
00:10:12,000 --> 00:10:13,000
[SPEAKER_00] Kao da visali ispred mene.

196
00:10:13,000 --> 00:10:14,000
[SPEAKER_00] Svi se...

197
00:10:14,000 --> 00:10:15,000
[SPEAKER_00] U jednu ruku ko sve stane.

198
00:10:15,000 --> 00:10:17,000
[SPEAKER_00] Sve se zacrni.

199
00:10:17,000 --> 00:10:21,000
[SPEAKER_00] I ostanemo samo ja i taj tekst.

200
00:10:21,000 --> 00:10:23,000
[SPEAKER_00] I ja gledam u njega.

201
00:10:23,000 --> 00:10:24,000
[SPEAKER_00] A ja osjetim.

202
00:10:24,000 --> 00:10:25,000
[SPEAKER_00] Ovo je živo. Ovo mene gleda.

203
00:10:25,000 --> 00:10:28,000
[SPEAKER_00] I slova su doslovno krenula izlaziti.

204
00:10:28,000 --> 00:10:33,000
[SPEAKER_00] Ja nisam znao da Bog može progovarati kroz vizije.

205
00:10:33,000 --> 00:10:36,000
[SPEAKER_00] Da može progovarati kroz svoju riječ.

206
00:10:36,000 --> 00:10:39,000
[SPEAKER_00] Nisam znao da sve može objaviti kome god hoće.

207
00:10:39,000 --> 00:10:40,000
[SPEAKER_00] Daš čini što god hoće.

208
00:10:40,000 --> 00:10:43,000
[SPEAKER_00] Zadnje što bi mislio da bi se meni objavio.

209
00:10:45,000 --> 00:10:48,000
[SPEAKER_00] Ako neko bio grešnik onda sam bio prvi i najveći među njima.

210
00:10:48,000 --> 00:10:50,000
[SPEAKER_00] I...

211
00:10:50,000 --> 00:10:54,000
[SPEAKER_00] Nakon toga sam osjetio duboki mir.

212
00:10:57,000 --> 00:11:02,000
[SPEAKER_00] I kasnije sam još nakon toga pokušao progovoriti s jedin svećenik.

213
00:11:02,000 --> 00:11:04,000
[SPEAKER_00] On me malo uputio o tome što mi se dešava.

214
00:11:08,000 --> 00:11:10,000
[SPEAKER_00] Nažalost nije doživio duhovno iskustvo na taj način.

215
00:11:10,000 --> 00:11:12,000
[SPEAKER_00] Bio je samo naučitelj.

216
00:11:12,000 --> 00:11:14,000
[SPEAKER_00] Ne govorim ništa proti svećenika.

217
00:11:14,000 --> 00:11:17,000
[SPEAKER_00] Neko ne bi nešto krivo protumačio.

218
00:11:17,000 --> 00:11:21,000
[SPEAKER_00] Nego govorim svoje iskustvo i evo čisto možda poticaj pastirima.

219
00:11:21,000 --> 00:11:24,000
[SPEAKER_00] Da ne otpile ljude tek tako lako.

220
00:11:25,000 --> 00:11:27,000
[SPEAKER_00] U tom trenutku on mislio da sam ja možda malo poludio.

221
00:11:27,000 --> 00:11:29,000
[SPEAKER_00] Da nisam normalan baš.

222
00:11:29,000 --> 00:11:31,000
[SPEAKER_00] I...

223
00:11:31,000 --> 00:11:34,000
[SPEAKER_00] Okej, ja sam otišao razočarao jedno njega.

224
00:11:34,000 --> 00:11:38,000
[SPEAKER_00] Ali sam nastavio razmišljati o Bogu i o tome što mi se sve dešavalo.

225
00:11:38,000 --> 00:11:40,000
[SPEAKER_00] Nisam odustao od potrege.

226
00:11:40,000 --> 00:11:43,000
[SPEAKER_00] I nedugo nakon toga Bog mi je dao jedan san.

227
00:11:43,000 --> 00:11:48,000
[SPEAKER_00] Sanjao sam svoju kuću, naselje, mjesto gdje živim.

228
00:11:48,000 --> 00:11:52,000
[SPEAKER_00] A ja sam bio kao izvan svog tijela.

229
00:11:53,000 --> 00:11:57,000
[SPEAKER_00] Bio sam visoko na nebu i sve sam vidio iz ptiće perspektive.

230
00:11:57,000 --> 00:12:06,000
[SPEAKER_00] U jednom trenutku, sve to što sam vidio, cijela zemlja se zatresla.

231
00:12:06,000 --> 00:12:08,000
[SPEAKER_00] Raspukao na jednom dijelu.

232
00:12:08,000 --> 00:12:13,000
[SPEAKER_00] I izbio je kao neki drevni hram koji je bio u vatri.

233
00:12:13,000 --> 00:12:16,000
[SPEAKER_00] A iz njega je izašao Sotona.

234
00:12:19,000 --> 00:12:24,000
[SPEAKER_00] U tom mom snu je izgledao kao što ga prikazuju u filmu "Pasija".

235
00:12:24,000 --> 00:12:30,000
[SPEAKER_00] Skroz bijel, onako, bljed, jezivo i prekriven kapuljačom.

236
00:12:31,000 --> 00:12:42,000
[SPEAKER_00] I osjećao sam strašno zlu prisutnost, strah, mržnju i sve ono što on nosi i što on je.

237
00:12:44,000 --> 00:12:46,000
[SPEAKER_00] I obilaze je oko kuća.

238
00:12:46,000 --> 00:12:52,000
[SPEAKER_00] A riječ Božja kaže da je Sotona došao, poput ričuće glava, tražeći koga da proštre.

239
00:12:52,000 --> 00:12:56,000
[SPEAKER_00] Da je došao ubiti, uništiti, ukrasti.

240
00:12:58,000 --> 00:13:03,000
[SPEAKER_00] Sljedeća scena koji sam vidio je da je došao do moje kuće, do moje obitelji.

241
00:13:03,000 --> 00:13:05,000
[SPEAKER_00] Da su mi krenjeli bježati.

242
00:13:05,000 --> 00:13:12,000
[SPEAKER_00] I njih je progutao dim i oganj, a on se luđački smijao.

243
00:13:13,000 --> 00:13:18,000
[SPEAKER_00] Ja sam nekako uspio pobjeći i dok sam bježao upao sam u rupu.

244
00:13:18,000 --> 00:13:22,000
[SPEAKER_00] Iduća scena, gledao sam sebe kako sam u toj rupi.

245
00:13:22,000 --> 00:13:24,000
[SPEAKER_00] Bio sam sav prljav.

246
00:13:24,000 --> 00:13:29,000
[SPEAKER_00] Rupa je bila jako visoka, nisam mogao izaći.

247
00:13:29,000 --> 00:13:32,000
[SPEAKER_00] A u ruci mi se našao joint.

248
00:13:32,000 --> 00:13:36,000
[SPEAKER_00] I tu mi je Bog progovarao:

249
00:13:36,000 --> 00:13:39,000
[SPEAKER_00] "Rop si svojih grijeha.

250
00:13:39,000 --> 00:13:41,000
[SPEAKER_00] Dođi meni da te oslobodim.

251
00:13:42,000 --> 00:13:44,000
[SPEAKER_00] Traži me dok me možeš naći.

252
00:13:44,000 --> 00:13:47,000
[SPEAKER_00] Da ne bude prekasno.

253
00:13:47,000 --> 00:13:51,000
[SPEAKER_00] Dođi me da te oslobodim."

254
00:13:51,000 --> 00:13:55,000
[SPEAKER_00] Tada je san završio.

255
00:13:55,000 --> 00:13:59,000
[SPEAKER_00] Ja sam bio jako uplašen i prestravljen.

256
00:13:59,000 --> 00:14:01,000
[SPEAKER_00] Nakon tog zna.

257
00:14:01,000 --> 00:14:03,000
[SPEAKER_00] Veliki strah sam osjećao.

258
00:14:03,000 --> 00:14:05,000
[SPEAKER_00] I vjerujem da je

259
00:14:05,000 --> 00:14:09,000
[SPEAKER_00] tada je jedan mali dio straha Božjega bio

260
00:14:09,000 --> 00:14:11,000
[SPEAKER_00] ulijeveno moj duh, moj dušu.

261
00:14:11,000 --> 00:14:14,000
[SPEAKER_00] Da me to potaklo da se vratim.

262
00:14:14,000 --> 00:14:17,000
[SPEAKER_00] I još jednom potražim pomoć u crkvi.

263
00:14:17,000 --> 00:14:21,000
[SPEAKER_00] A omeđu vremenu sam

264
00:14:21,000 --> 00:14:25,000
[SPEAKER_00] tam prije ili taj dan čak

265
00:14:25,000 --> 00:14:27,000
[SPEAKER_00] saznao da postoji molitva oslobođenja

266
00:14:27,000 --> 00:14:30,000
[SPEAKER_00] i da se neko treba pomoliti za mene.

267
00:14:30,000 --> 00:14:32,000
[SPEAKER_00] Da slomi utjece zloga u mom životu.

268
00:14:33,000 --> 00:14:35,000
[SPEAKER_00] i da se trebam ispovijediti.

269
00:14:35,000 --> 00:14:42,000
[SPEAKER_00] Došao sam u crkvu i zamolio svećenika da se pomoli za mene.

270
00:14:43,000 --> 00:14:45,000
[SPEAKER_00] rekao sam mu

271
00:14:45,000 --> 00:14:47,000
[SPEAKER_00] da ne znam šta mi se dešava.

272
00:14:47,000 --> 00:14:50,000
[SPEAKER_00] Da me zlo dusio neki progonu.

273
00:14:50,000 --> 00:14:51,000
[SPEAKER_00] Nije mi ništa jasno šta vidim.

274
00:14:54,000 --> 00:14:56,000
[SPEAKER_00] Valja ti znaš tog Boga.

275
00:14:56,000 --> 00:14:57,000
[SPEAKER_00] A mi molim te pomozi.

276
00:14:57,000 --> 00:15:00,000
[SPEAKER_00] On je tada rekao da

277
00:15:00,000 --> 00:15:04,000
[SPEAKER_00] imao je goste iz drugog mjesta koji su mu držali duhovnu obnovu.

278
00:15:06,000 --> 00:15:07,000
[SPEAKER_00] I rekao je

279
00:15:07,000 --> 00:15:08,000
[SPEAKER_00] ajde mom te dođi sutra

280
00:15:08,000 --> 00:15:09,000
[SPEAKER_00] ali neki drugi dan.

281
00:15:09,000 --> 00:15:10,000
[SPEAKER_00] Ne mogu baš sada.

282
00:15:10,000 --> 00:15:11,000
[SPEAKER_00] Nezgodno mi je.

283
00:15:11,000 --> 00:15:12,000
[SPEAKER_00] Rekao ok.

284
00:15:12,000 --> 00:15:15,000
[SPEAKER_00] A bio sam razočaran naravno time.

285
00:15:15,000 --> 00:15:17,000
[SPEAKER_00] I očista naglasim

286
00:15:17,000 --> 00:15:18,000
[SPEAKER_00] dobar sam prijatelj.

287
00:15:18,000 --> 00:15:20,000
[SPEAKER_00] Danas se oba ta svećenika iz priče.

288
00:15:20,000 --> 00:15:24,000
[SPEAKER_00] Bog je sve izvio na dobro.

289
00:15:24,000 --> 00:15:27,000
[SPEAKER_00] I kada sam izašao iz crkve

290
00:15:27,000 --> 00:15:32,000
[SPEAKER_00] rekao izgubljen šta sad kud sada opet da idem.

291
00:15:32,000 --> 00:15:35,000
[SPEAKER_00] I vidio sam dvojicu mamaka koji su

292
00:15:36,000 --> 00:15:40,000
[SPEAKER_00] sve među vremenu ja sam ih poznavao iz izlazaka i škole neke.

293
00:15:40,000 --> 00:15:42,000
[SPEAKER_00] Ali oni su se obratili među vremenu.

294
00:15:42,000 --> 00:15:46,000
[SPEAKER_00] I postali su članovi doma molitve.

295
00:15:46,000 --> 00:15:51,000
[SPEAKER_00] A u doma molitve se tada dešavala

296
00:15:51,000 --> 00:15:52,000
[SPEAKER_00] uzistom tom periodu.

297
00:15:52,000 --> 00:15:54,000
[SPEAKER_00] U tom terminu.

298
00:15:54,000 --> 00:15:55,000
[SPEAKER_00] U tim satima.

299
00:15:55,000 --> 00:15:57,000
[SPEAKER_00] Zagovorna molitva.

300
00:15:57,000 --> 00:16:01,000
[SPEAKER_00] I oni su molili da Bog dotakne mlade ljude.

301
00:16:01,000 --> 00:16:03,000
[SPEAKER_00] Da ih obasja svojim svijetlom.

302
00:16:03,000 --> 00:16:04,000
[SPEAKER_00] Da im se objavi.

303
00:16:05,000 --> 00:16:07,000
[SPEAKER_00] Da im objavi svrhu za njihov život.

304
00:16:07,000 --> 00:16:09,000
[SPEAKER_00] Da ih oslobozi od zloga.

305
00:16:09,000 --> 00:16:10,000
[SPEAKER_00] Da im objavi ko on je.

306
00:16:10,000 --> 00:16:12,000
[SPEAKER_00] Da im otvori oči srca.

307
00:16:12,000 --> 00:16:15,000
[SPEAKER_00] Da ih prebaci u svoje kraljevstvo.

308
00:16:15,000 --> 00:16:17,000
[SPEAKER_00] Da ih učini svojom djecom.

309
00:16:17,000 --> 00:16:21,000
[SPEAKER_00] I ta molitva je.

310
00:16:21,000 --> 00:16:23,000
[SPEAKER_00] Bogu hvala.

311
00:16:23,000 --> 00:16:24,000
[SPEAKER_00] ovocirala.

312
00:16:24,000 --> 00:16:26,000
[SPEAKER_00] I krenila je.

313
00:16:26,000 --> 00:16:28,000
[SPEAKER_00] Voditi moj put do doma molitve.

314
00:16:28,000 --> 00:16:29,000
[SPEAKER_00] Jer došao sam.

315
00:16:29,000 --> 00:16:31,000
[SPEAKER_00] Ja gledam tu dvojicu momaka.

316
00:16:31,000 --> 00:16:34,000
[SPEAKER_00] Gledaju oni u mene.

317
00:16:34,000 --> 00:16:36,000
[SPEAKER_00] Šta ćete vi ovdje?

318
00:16:36,000 --> 00:16:37,000
[SPEAKER_00] Gledaju u mene.

319
00:16:37,000 --> 00:16:38,000
[SPEAKER_00] Štaš ti tu?

320
00:16:38,000 --> 00:16:42,000
[SPEAKER_00] Jer smo se poznavali iz drugih okolnosti.

321
00:16:45,000 --> 00:16:47,000
[SPEAKER_00] I tad nisam znao zašto.

322
00:16:47,000 --> 00:16:51,000
[SPEAKER_00] Ali sad znam jer molilo se o tom trenutku.

323
00:16:51,000 --> 00:16:55,000
[SPEAKER_00] Otvorio sam im svoje srce i rekao.

324
00:16:57,000 --> 00:16:59,000
[SPEAKER_00] Ne znam što mi se dešava.

325
00:16:59,000 --> 00:17:02,000
[SPEAKER_00] Mani neko treba pomoći.

326
00:17:02,000 --> 00:17:04,000
[SPEAKER_00] Neki zlodosi me progone.

327
00:17:04,000 --> 00:17:05,000
[SPEAKER_00] Guše me.

328
00:17:05,000 --> 00:17:06,000
[SPEAKER_00] Ne mogu spavati.

329
00:17:06,000 --> 00:17:08,000
[SPEAKER_00] Ne znam što da radim.

330
00:17:08,000 --> 00:17:09,000
[SPEAKER_00] Nema mira.

331
00:17:09,000 --> 00:17:12,000
[SPEAKER_00] Ne znam više li sam normalan ili nisam.

332
00:17:12,000 --> 00:17:14,000
[SPEAKER_00] Ne znam kome da se obratim.

333
00:17:14,000 --> 00:17:16,000
[SPEAKER_00] Nisam našao kom još može pomoći.

334
00:17:16,000 --> 00:17:18,000
[SPEAKER_00] I oni su samo pogadali i rekli:

335
00:17:18,000 --> 00:17:20,000
[SPEAKER_00] "Hajde s nama na jedno mjesto."

336
00:17:20,000 --> 00:17:21,000
[SPEAKER_00] "Ojde."

337
00:17:21,000 --> 00:17:25,000
[SPEAKER_00] I vozili se mi u doma molitve.

338
00:17:26,000 --> 00:17:28,000
[SPEAKER_00] I putem kaže: "Ovo je meni jedan."

339
00:17:28,000 --> 00:17:30,000
[SPEAKER_00] "E slušaj, kad dođeš tamo.

340
00:17:30,000 --> 00:17:33,000
[SPEAKER_00] Budi skroz slobodna ako ti dođe da plaćeš.

341
00:17:33,000 --> 00:17:35,000
[SPEAKER_00] Sam se opusti.

342
00:17:35,000 --> 00:17:36,000
[SPEAKER_00] Nemoj se sudržavati."

343
00:17:36,000 --> 00:17:38,000
[SPEAKER_00] Ja stao gledam u njega.

344
00:17:38,000 --> 00:17:41,000
[SPEAKER_00] "Bat ću ti ja plakat ono muškarčina da plaće."

345
00:17:41,000 --> 00:17:45,000
[SPEAKER_00] I...

346
00:17:45,000 --> 00:17:49,000
[SPEAKER_00] Odvedeli su me gore.

347
00:17:49,000 --> 00:17:51,000
[SPEAKER_00] Zagovora molitva je trajala.

348
00:17:51,000 --> 00:17:53,000
[SPEAKER_00] To će biti ono što će ovdje sad biti.

349
00:17:53,000 --> 00:17:55,000
[SPEAKER_00] Ta harpa i čaša, taj model molitve.

350
00:17:55,000 --> 00:17:57,000
[SPEAKER_00] Trajala je od osam do deset.

351
00:17:57,000 --> 00:17:58,000
[SPEAKER_00] Bilo je pet do deset.

352
00:17:58,000 --> 00:18:00,000
[SPEAKER_00] Ja ušao u sobu.

353
00:18:00,000 --> 00:18:02,000
[SPEAKER_00] Karizmatska zajednica, da naglasim.

354
00:18:02,000 --> 00:18:05,000
[SPEAKER_00] Gledam, ovi tamo pjevaju.

355
00:18:05,000 --> 00:18:07,000
[SPEAKER_00] Slave.

356
00:18:07,000 --> 00:18:09,000
[SPEAKER_00] Ovaj na podu plaće.

357
00:18:09,000 --> 00:18:14,000
[SPEAKER_00] Ovaj od sreće hoće pukenut od smijeha.

358
00:18:15,000 --> 00:18:18,000
[SPEAKER_00] Šta je ovo ovdje svako u svom filmu?

359
00:18:18,000 --> 00:18:20,000
[SPEAKER_00] Ali svidjelo mi se.

360
00:18:20,000 --> 00:18:24,000
[SPEAKER_00] Jer društvo koje sam ja navikao biti...

361
00:18:24,000 --> 00:18:26,000
[SPEAKER_00] Ljudi su bili jako hladni.

362
00:18:26,000 --> 00:18:28,000
[SPEAKER_00] Većinom iz teških okolnosti.

363
00:18:28,000 --> 00:18:30,000
[SPEAKER_00] I...

364
00:18:30,000 --> 00:18:34,000
[SPEAKER_00] Jednostavno uvijek su nosili svoje maske i niko nije pokazivao slabosti i osjećaje.

365
00:18:35,000 --> 00:18:38,000
[SPEAKER_00] Dok je ovdje bilo drugačiji ljudi su bili jako otvoreni za to.

366
00:18:38,000 --> 00:18:42,000
[SPEAKER_00] I naprijed bio samo jedan...

367
00:18:42,000 --> 00:18:44,000
[SPEAKER_00] Pramladi čovjek.

368
00:18:44,000 --> 00:18:46,000
[SPEAKER_00] Malo stari.

369
00:18:47,000 --> 00:18:49,000
[SPEAKER_00] Tu voditelj doma molitve Bartlu Pešorda i...

370
00:18:49,000 --> 00:18:54,000
[SPEAKER_00] Njiše se on na stolcu. Njiše se on, njiše. Njiše se, njiše.

371
00:18:54,000 --> 00:18:57,000
[SPEAKER_00] Reko: "Otkud ovaj ovdje? Ovo je garan glavni."

372
00:18:57,000 --> 00:19:01,000
[SPEAKER_00] I...

373
00:19:01,000 --> 00:19:05,000
[SPEAKER_00] Termin je nakon par minuta završio i Bartle je samo došao do mene.

374
00:19:05,000 --> 00:19:07,000
[SPEAKER_00] "Bito me, što želiš?"

375
00:19:07,000 --> 00:19:10,000
[SPEAKER_00] Ja sam rekao da mu se oduprem.

376
00:19:10,000 --> 00:19:13,000
[SPEAKER_00] Da se oduprem sa to ne to znači.

377
00:19:13,000 --> 00:19:15,000
[SPEAKER_00] U istom trenutku...

378
00:19:16,000 --> 00:19:21,000
[SPEAKER_00] Nije šansa da me dotakao, samo je Digo Ruh hrenio prema meni.

379
00:19:21,000 --> 00:19:27,000
[SPEAKER_00] Dusveti se tako snažno spustio na mene.

380
00:19:27,000 --> 00:19:30,000
[SPEAKER_00] Tako duboko pohajanje sam osjećao.

381
00:19:30,000 --> 00:19:36,000
[SPEAKER_00] Srce raskaljeno, ponizno do kraja, srušeno, slomljeno.

382
00:19:36,000 --> 00:19:40,000
[SPEAKER_00] Bog mi tad snažno pohodio i...

383
00:19:40,000 --> 00:19:44,000
[SPEAKER_00] Po prvi put u životu mogu reći da sam osjetio da sam ljubljen.

384
00:19:45,000 --> 00:19:49,000
[SPEAKER_00] Kako je ta Boža ljubav prodirala u mene.

385
00:19:49,000 --> 00:19:55,000
[SPEAKER_00] Plakao sam, revao sam sat i po dva, rekao sam da neću plakat.

386
00:19:58,000 --> 00:20:02,000
[SPEAKER_00] toliko od toga je izlazilo iz mene tih.

387
00:20:02,000 --> 00:20:06,000
[SPEAKER_00] I toliko od toga je Bog liječio meni i oslobađao me.

388
00:20:07,000 --> 00:20:16,000
[SPEAKER_00] Ono u bolnici, kad me Bog izcijelio i pohodio, za to volim reći da je to prvi put da sam susreo Boga.

389
00:20:17,000 --> 00:20:22,000
[SPEAKER_00] A ovo u domu molitve je bio prvi put da sam ga upoznao.

390
00:20:22,000 --> 00:20:31,000
[SPEAKER_00] Tad sam spoznao da je to Isus i da je On bio cijelo vrijeme taj koji me ozdravio i koji nije dao džavu da oduzme moj život.

391
00:20:32,000 --> 00:20:35,000
[SPEAKER_00] Koji mi je skazao milosti ako ja to ničem nisam zaslužio.

392
00:20:35,000 --> 00:20:38,000
[SPEAKER_00] Koji mi je sve oprostio.

393
00:20:40,000 --> 00:20:52,000
[SPEAKER_00] Oslobodio me od marihuane, cigareta, izlazaka, alkohola, psovanja, pornografije, gledanja televizora.

394
00:20:52,000 --> 00:20:55,000
[SPEAKER_00] Toliko toga.

395
00:20:55,000 --> 00:21:01,000
[SPEAKER_00] Toliko toga je Bog radikalno počeo mijenjati u mom životu.

396
00:21:07,000 --> 00:21:17,000
[SPEAKER_00] I tada kada sam spoznao da ako postoji Bog, onda je On najbitniji.

397
00:21:17,000 --> 00:21:21,000
[SPEAKER_00] A ako ne postoji, ništa drugo nije bitno.

398
00:21:21,000 --> 00:21:28,000
[SPEAKER_00] I osjetio sam duboku rupu u sebi.

399
00:21:28,000 --> 00:21:34,000
[SPEAKER_00] Da koju stvarno vjerujem da je to Bogom dan i prostor u svakom čovjeku.

400
00:21:36,000 --> 00:21:38,000
[SPEAKER_00] Koji samo On može ispuniti.

401
00:21:38,000 --> 00:21:40,000
[SPEAKER_00] I niko drugi ništa drugo.

402
00:21:40,000 --> 00:21:43,000
[SPEAKER_00] Do li dug Boži i Božja prisutnost.

403
00:21:43,000 --> 00:21:55,000
[SPEAKER_00] Ta glad za Bogom, mogu reći, je najveći blagoslov koji mi je dao od samog početka.

404
00:21:55,000 --> 00:21:58,000
[SPEAKER_00] Glad za Bogom i odnos sa Bogom.

405
00:22:02,000 --> 00:22:09,000
[SPEAKER_00] Dan danas na ga, zahvaljujući njemu, jednako glada, ako ne i više.

406
00:22:13,000 --> 00:22:21,000
[SPEAKER_00] I mogu vam reći po svom putu, kako je to izgledalo ovi sedam godina u vrijednoj rečenici, ovo je sedma.

407
00:22:21,000 --> 00:22:27,000
[SPEAKER_00] Da prve tri godine je bilo intenzivno upoznavanje Boga.

408
00:22:27,000 --> 00:22:31,000
[SPEAKER_00] Druge tri godine je jako puno bilo upoznavanja i ispoznavanja sebe.

409
00:22:31,000 --> 00:22:36,000
[SPEAKER_00] Svega onoga što u sebi treba popraviti i mijenjati.

410
00:22:36,000 --> 00:22:37,000
[SPEAKER_00] Toliko je toga.

411
00:22:38,000 --> 00:22:41,000
[SPEAKER_00] I ovo je daleko najteža godina koju sam imao.

412
00:22:41,000 --> 00:22:43,000
[SPEAKER_00] I samo Božja milost mi održala.

413
00:22:43,000 --> 00:22:46,000
[SPEAKER_00] Samo to što sam bio do njegovi nogu.

414
00:22:46,000 --> 00:22:49,000
[SPEAKER_00] Bez toga nema šanse da bi uspio.

415
00:22:52,000 --> 00:22:59,000
[SPEAKER_00] I stvarno vam želim svima da se otvorite Božim djelovanjem, da se opredijelite za njega.

416
00:22:59,000 --> 00:23:04,000
[SPEAKER_00] Ne znamo niko kad ćemo umrijeti.

417
00:23:04,000 --> 00:23:09,000
[SPEAKER_00] Nažalost, može se desiti, nek nas Bog sve očuva, već sada kad neko bude išao kući.

418
00:23:09,000 --> 00:23:16,000
[SPEAKER_00] I tad vam neće biti vrijedan ni vaš auto, ni firma, ni karijera, ništa.

419
00:23:16,000 --> 00:23:20,000
[SPEAKER_00] Samo vaš odnos s Bogom.

420
00:23:20,000 --> 00:23:22,000
[SPEAKER_00] Jeste li upoznali Boga?

421
00:23:22,000 --> 00:23:24,000
[SPEAKER_00] Jeste li ga uzljubili?

422
00:23:24,000 --> 00:23:29,000
[SPEAKER_00] I jeste li živjeli za njega i za njegove ciljeve?

423
00:23:29,000 --> 00:23:35,000
[SPEAKER_00] Ili ste živjeli za sebe i potrošili život u ispraznostima?

424
00:23:35,000 --> 00:23:41,000
[SPEAKER_00] Izaberite bolji dio ljudi.

425
00:23:41,000 --> 00:23:48,000
[SPEAKER_00] I evo za kraj, mi je volio pročitati jednu rečenicu koju sam zapisao.

426
00:23:48,000 --> 00:23:54,000
[SPEAKER_00] Nakon strašno bolnih situacija koje sam prošao, bio sam sav slobnjen.

427
00:23:54,000 --> 00:23:57,000
[SPEAKER_00] Tražio sam Boga i...

428
00:23:57,000 --> 00:24:05,000
[SPEAKER_00] Nakon nekih mjeseci i po dana, jako, jako bolnih molitava, bolnih iskustava.

429
00:24:06,000 --> 00:24:12,000
[SPEAKER_00] Dokodio je se odnaj trenutak koji je, ja volim reći da živim za take trenutke.

430
00:24:18,000 --> 00:24:25,000
[SPEAKER_00] Spoznajem da su u Božoj prisutnosti sve moje čežnje, želje i potrebe zadovoljene.

431
00:24:26,000 --> 00:24:28,000
[SPEAKER_00] Nemam drugih apetita.

432
00:24:28,000 --> 00:24:30,000
[SPEAKER_00] Svi ljudi postaju dosadni.

433
00:24:30,000 --> 00:24:34,000
[SPEAKER_00] Sve drugo postaje nebitno.

434
00:24:40,000 --> 00:24:43,000
[SPEAKER_00] On je put istine i život.

435
00:24:43,000 --> 00:24:45,000
[SPEAKER_00] Život vječni.

436
00:24:45,000 --> 00:24:49,000
[SPEAKER_00] A ovo je vječni život.

437
00:24:49,000 --> 00:24:55,000
[SPEAKER_00] Da upoznate Otca i Onoga koga je On poslao.

438
00:24:55,000 --> 00:24:57,000
[SPEAKER_00] Isusa Hrista.

439
00:24:57,000 --> 00:24:59,000
[SPEAKER_00] I da živite za Njega.

440
00:25:00,000 --> 00:25:00,240
[SPEAKER_00] Amen.

